      "rationale": "Titanium alloy (Ti-6Al-4V) modelled as bilinear isotropic hardening; elastic modulus and tangent modulus from manufacturer coupon data. UHMWPE vertebral body surrogates modelled as elastic-perfectly plastic per ASTM F1717 material specification. Augmented Lagrangian contact at screw-rod and rod-tulip interfaces. Model form assessed at level 3 consistent with medium risk and multi-material nonlinear contact physics."
