      "rationale": "Elastic modulus Ti-6Al-4V: 114 ± 3 GPa from n=5 tensile coupons (lot-matched). UHMWPE modulus: 0.95 ± 0.08 GPa from manufacturer data sheet. Screw outer diameter, pitch, and root radius from CMM (n=3 specimens, lab-calibrated). Uncertainty ranges propagated via Monte Carlo (n=1000 runs). Input uncertainty contribution to QoI uncertainty < 4%."
