      "rationale": "Testing performed at a single loading rate (5 mm/min) and ambient temperature (23 ± 2 °C) per ASTM F1717. The intended use envelope includes physiological loading rates and body temperature; these conditions were not explored. Achieved level 2 is below the required level 3. This gap is acknowledged and accepted given the conservative nature of quasi-static room-temperature testing for stiffness and yield force QoIs."
    },
