      "rationale": "Construct stiffness relates to load sharing and adjacent segment effects; yield force is the primary fatigue precursor metric; force at 40 mm displacement is the ASTM F1717 standard reporting requirement. All three QoIs are directly cited in the 510(k) special controls guidance for spinal fixation systems. Relevance confirmed at level 3."
